divs: Sighting Detailsfirst noticed in the northeast, heading to the southwest. shortly thereafter, it began to veer to the west and eventually to the northwest. flew at normal speed for an aircraft, but was much too large to be a normal airplane; basically reddish in color, but appeared to be ablaze. finally, it disappeared from sight in the northwest. witnessed by at least three people & was photographed.
Summary: glowing red as if on fire
